'''柏孜克里克千佛洞'''（{{lang-ug|بېزەكلىك بۇددا غارلىرى}}；[[拉丁维文|拉丁维文]]：Bëzeklik Budda Gharliri），位于中国[[新疆维吾尔自治区|新疆维吾尔自治区]][[吐鲁番市|吐鲁番市]]{{tsl|en|Mutou Valley|木头沟}}，是[[第二批全国重点文物保护单位|第二批全国重点文物保护单位]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2009-10/03/content_12177200.htm |title=新疆吐鲁番柏孜克里克千佛洞首次发现地画 |access-date=2010-01-08 |archive-date=2010-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101022122308/http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2009-10/03/content_12177200.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 介绍 ==
它始凿于[[南北朝|南北朝]]晚期，为[[高昌|高昌]]地区的[[佛教|佛教]]中心<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.chinahighlights.com/xinjiang/turpan/attraction/bezeklik-thousand-buddha-caves.htm
 |title       = Bezeklik Thousand Buddha Caves
 |publisher   = chinahighlights.com
 |accessdate  = 2007-09-19
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20071014055235/http://www.chinahighlights.com/xinjiang/turpan/attraction/bezeklik-thousand-buddha-caves.htm
 |archivedate = 2007-10-14
}}</ref><ref>{{cite web
|year=
|month=
|url=http://www.travelchinaguide.com/attraction/xinjiang/turpan/bizaklik.htm
|title=Bizaklik Thousand Buddha Caves
|publisher=travelchinaguide.com
|accessdate=2007-09-21
|archive-date=2019-11-29
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129052336/https://www.travelchinaguide.com/attraction/xinjiang/turpan/bizaklik.htm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。其佛洞现存57个，其中40个还存壁画，内容大多描述佛教故事及佛像，其中还有[[摩尼教|摩尼教]]洞窟、壁画，是世上少有的保留摩尼教文化场所。它也是吐鲁番现存洞窟最多、壁画内容最丰富的石窟群<ref>{{cite web
|year=
|month=
|url=http://www.showcaves.com/english/cn/misc/Bezeklik.html
|title=Bizaklik Thousand Buddha Caves
|publisher=showcaves.com
|accessdate=2007-09-21
|archive-date=2018-05-03
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180503002657/http://www.showcaves.com/english/cn/misc/Bezeklik.html
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

